{"3903880": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "NTR介紹所", "steam_appid": 3903880, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/36b81d19dee489893465704c1430161f.poster.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/36b81d19dee489893465704c1430161f.webm?t=1765209441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的女朋友相戀已久，她不僅是你最親密的戀人，也是你的青梅竹馬。現在的你們正一起努力過著幸福的生活，你要在工作，信任，和溝通之間找到平衡，用行動去守護這段感情。你的每一個決定，都會影響你們的未來，是幸福美滿，還是慢慢變淡，全看你怎麼選擇了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/8fa2bea59a6534cc50304e99bb944769.poster.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/8fa2bea59a6534cc50304e99bb944769.webm?t=1765209441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款戀愛模擬遊戲裡，你需要經營自己的日常生活。每天你都得在有限的時間裡做好安排：是拼命打工賺錢？還是給女友打電話維繫感情？又或者一個人發呆，看著相冊回憶從前？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一次選擇都會影響跟她的關係走向。用心維繫，她會越來越愛你；但如果忽視了她，那份感情也可能逐漸消退。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/34c1a9328df7202c6e2c5b8c496293b1.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/71cc2770a4b4915514fa235b11b7406d.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/43ef37ef60a1d80ae44af7cd6a1bb4b5.poster.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/43ef37ef60a1d80ae44af7cd6a1bb4b5.webm?t=1765209441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>時間管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在打工，打電話，和回憶過去之間合理安排。每一個選擇都會直接影響你們的關係。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多個結局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你們關係的走向取決於你的選擇。也許你們會一直幸福地在一起，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可能因為疏遠誤會，慢慢走向分離。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>黑白畫風</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲採用黑白藝術風格，簡潔獨特的同時，也能更專注於劇情與情感的表達。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>命名系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自由設置主角和女朋友的名字。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/36b81d19dee489893465704c1430161f.poster.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/36b81d19dee489893465704c1430161f.webm?t=1765209441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的女朋友相戀已久，她不僅是你最親密的戀人，也是你的青梅竹馬。現在的你們正一起努力過著幸福的生活，你要在工作，信任，和溝通之間找到平衡，用行動去守護這段感情。你的每一個決定，都會影響你們的未來，是幸福美滿，還是慢慢變淡，全看你怎麼選擇了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/8fa2bea59a6534cc50304e99bb944769.poster.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/8fa2bea59a6534cc50304e99bb944769.webm?t=1765209441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款戀愛模擬遊戲裡，你需要經營自己的日常生活。每天你都得在有限的時間裡做好安排：是拼命打工賺錢？還是給女友打電話維繫感情？又或者一個人發呆，看著相冊回憶從前？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一次選擇都會影響跟她的關係走向。用心維繫，她會越來越愛你；但如果忽視了她，那份感情也可能逐漸消退。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/34c1a9328df7202c6e2c5b8c496293b1.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/71cc2770a4b4915514fa235b11b7406d.avif?t=1765209441\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903880/extras/43ef37ef60a1d80ae44af7cd6a1bb4b